# **Step 4: TCPDF Setup & PDF Create â€” Simple Wording**

---

## **Step 4.1: TCPDF Instance Create Karna**

```php
$pdf = new TCPDF('P', 'mm', 'A4', true, 'UTF-8', false);
```

**Simple words:**

* `'P'` â†’ Portrait page
* `'mm'` â†’ Measurement in millimeters
* `'A4'` â†’ Page size
* `'UTF-8'` â†’ Text encoding
* Ye line **PDF create kar rahi hai**.

---

## **Step 4.2: PDF Title & Font Set Karna**

```php
$pdf->SetTitle(translate($data['meta']['title'], 'ur'));
$pdf->SetFont($data['meta']['font'], '', 12);
```

**Simple words:**

* `SetTitle` â†’ PDF ka title set kare
* `SetFont` â†’ PDF me font aur size set kare
* Yaha translation function Urdu me apply ho raha hai.

---

## **Step 4.3: Page Add Karna**

```php
$pdf->AddPage();
```

**Simple words:**

* Ek naya page PDF me add karo

---

## **Step 4.4: Header Text Add Karna**

```php
foreach($data['header']['items'] as $item) {
    $pdf->Write(6, translate($item['value'], 'ur'), '', 0, 'L', true, 0, false, false, 0);
}
```

**Simple words:**

* Header me har line text show karo
* Translation Urdu me apply karo
* `6` â†’ line height
* `'L'` â†’ text left align

---

## **Step 4.5: Hero Section Add Karna**

```php
if($data['hero_section']['enabled']) {
    foreach($data['hero_section']['items'] as $item) {
        $pdf->Write(6, translate($item['value'], 'ur'), '', 0, 'L', true, 0, false, false, 0);
    }
}
```

**Simple words:**

* Hero section ek special box hota hai
* Agar enabled hai to uske text lines PDF me show karo

---

## **Step 4.6: Body Table Add Karna**

```php
$table_html = '<table border="1" cellpadding="4"><tr>';
foreach($data['body']['table']['headers'] as $header) {
    $table_html .= '<th>' . translate($header['label'], 'ur') . '</th>';
}
$table_html .= '</tr>';
foreach($data['body']['table']['rows'] as $row) {
    $table_html .= '<tr>';
    foreach($data['body']['table']['headers'] as $header) {
        $key = $header['key'];
        $table_html .= '<td>' . $row[$key] . '</td>';
    }
    $table_html .= '</tr>';
}
$table_html .= '</table>';
$pdf->writeHTML($table_html, true, false, false, false, '');
```

**Simple words:**

1. Table start karo (`<table>` tag)
2. Table headers add karo
3. Table rows add karo (JSON ke data se)
4. `writeHTML` â†’ PDF me table show karo

---

## **Step 4.7: Footer Add Karna**

```php
foreach($data['footer']['items'] as $item) {
    if($item['type'] == 'text') {
        $pdf->Write(6, translate($item['value'], 'ur'), '', 0, 'C', true, 0, false, false, 0);
    }
    if($item['type'] == 'logo') {
        $pdf->Image(public_path($item['path']), '', '', 30, 15);
    }
}
```

**Simple words:**

* Footer me **text** aur **logo** add karo
* Text center align (`'C'`)
* Logo ka size 30x15 mm

---

## **Step 4.8: PDF Output Karna**

```php
$pdf->Output('report.pdf', 'I');
```

**Simple words:**

* PDF browser me open ho jayega
* File name = `report.pdf`

